evidence.source_document: Complaint for Declaratory and Injunctive Relief
evidence.text: This Court has jurisdiction over this action pursuant to 28 U.S.C. §§ 1331 and 1361.
The Court denies the motion for an administrative stay and a stay pending appeal (ECF 13) in this case.

evidence.source_document: Complaint for Declaratory and Injunctive Relief
evidence.text: Plaintiffs have a non-statutory right of action to enjoin and declare unlawful official action that is ultra vires and in excess of legal authority.
